What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Off the Road (OTR) Tires Market?

Market Analysis and Insights:

Global Off the Road (OTR) Tires Market

The off the road (OTR) tires market size is valued at USD 9.06 billion by 2028 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 5.50% over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on off the road (OTR) tires market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth.

Off the road tires are specially designed to enhance the performance and stability and also provide traction on different unpaved surfaces such as sand, mud, dirt among others. OTR tires are broadly used at civil engineering sites, dam construction sites, sand and gravel at mining, agriculture sector and others.

The off the road (OTR) tires market has a huge potential and is expected grow over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028, owing to the rise in industrialization and rapid urbanization particularly in developing countries. In addition, the high demand for modern agriculture vehicles across the world and the rise in the farm mechanization especially in emerging economies are also largely influencing the growth of the off the road (OTR) tires market. Also the rise in government subsidies on many agriculture equipments and machinery resulting in high demand for OTR tires across the globe is another driver anticipated to flourish the off the road (OTR) tires market growth. Additionally, the high demand for Off-highway vehicles in developed and developing countries and increase in the construction activities across the globe are also expected to boost the growth of the off the road (OTR) tires market in the above mentioned forecast period.

However, the market of off the road (OTR) tires though has certain limitations which are expected to obstruct the potential growth of the market such as the fluctuating raw material prices and rise in the gap between OTR tires demand and supply, whereas the extreme weather conditions and customization can challenge the growth of the off the road (OTR) tires market in the above mentioned forecast period.

In addition, the rapid increase in the OTR tire manufacturers focus on the production of eco-friendly OTR tires and high investment in research and development activities are projected to offer various growth opportunities for the off the road (OTR) tires market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

